author: Lucy Nicholson
title: Sign of the times: Mile-long line of cars outside California grocery giveaway
description: A pop-up food pantry in Southern California on Thursday drew so many people that the line of cars waiting for free groceries stretched about a mile (1.6 km), a haunting sign of how the coronavirus pandemic has hurt the working poor.
